	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Two things to check: <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha"><li>Some converters require the NES cartridge to be facing backward. Make sure it's facing the way the converter's label says. </li><li><a href="http://stoneagegamer.com/nestofamicomconverter72-pinto60-pin.aspx" class="postlink">The product page</a> says it has trouble with AV Famicom. Do other NES games work? </li><li>Is it an authentic AV Famicom? Some famiclones can't run the PowerPak at all. </li></ol>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


